$t[3] = 'Na wamechukua badala yake miungu ambayo haiumbi chochote, bali hiyo inaumbwa, haijimilikii nafsi zao madhara wala manufaa, wala haimiliki mauti, wala uhai, wala kufufuka.';
$t[4] = 'Na wamesema walio kufuru: Haya si chochote ila ni uzushi alio uzua, na wamemsaidia kwa haya watu wengine! Hakika hawa wamekuja na dhulma na uwongo.';
